parameters:
\n< Serena >I can't concentrate on reading with this kind of
outfit...

\n< Female >It seems that slimes inhabit near the spirit
grass. Please be careful, okay?

\n< Serena >I'm back. Here is the grass I procured. I want you
to confirm it.

\n< Female >Oh, you're back quite early. As expected, you're
someone I have my eye on. You're truly excellent.
\n< Female >Please wait a moment. Pokedex, Pokedex... umm...
\n< Serena >I have one question, what exactly is that grass?
\n< Female >...I wonder what that means?
\n< Serena >It's nothing. I was just curious, that's all.

\n< Female >...This grass grows by sucking the lifeblood of
humans.

\n< Female >Deep in the dimly lit and miasma-filled forest...
When frost falls and mist rises, demons come to
place sacrifices.

\n< Female >When the grass bed envelops the sacrifice, the
five bodies disappear into the ground and the next
morning, a beautiful flower blooms...
\n< Serena >It's a creepy ecology.

\n< Female >Ohoho, it's just a tasteless legend. Ah, even the
base of these petals matches perfectly.

\n< Female >There is no mistake. Thank you, little adventurer.
With this, the request is complete.
\n< Serena >Hmm. Then I'll sign here... That's right.

\n< Serena >...But if that's the case, does that mean the
human I encountered deep in the forest was one of
those demons?
\n< Female >Oh, did you meet someone?

\n< Serena >Hmm. She was a young woman with a somewhat
indifferent atmosphere.

\n< Serena >The women were diligently plucking that grass. But
despite that, they said it was unnecessary. Thanks
to that, I was able to get it from them.
\n< Female >Oh, oh, well... that is... I see...

\n< Female >Surely, she must have been a woman as sinful as a
demon.
\n< Serena >....

\n< Serena >Well, it's pointless to think about it. Anyway,
this is the last \V[2501] remaining... just a
little more.
'　何が何やらわからぬが、とにかく目的は達した。宿へ戻って今日は休もう。'

events.name: ユニコーンの鞍　依頼ドア

parameters: \n< Serena >Are you ready?
\n< Female >Eek!

\n< Serena >Are you the one who received the request from the
guild, without a doubt?
\n< Female >Huh? Uh... um, yes... but why?
\n< Serena >I would like to hear the details!

\n< Female >Ah, I wonder if you're an adventurer...? In that
case, please come in and have a seat here, if you
would.
\n< Serena >I'm here to intrude!
\n< Female >That's the reason.
\n< Serena >Haaaahhhh.......
\n< Female >I wonder what happened?

\n< Serena >No... it's nothing. I just had my own
expectations... and they didn't pan out.

\n< Serena >To summarize the story... you were engaged to a
certain nobleman from the city.

\n< Serena >I explained to my partner that I have no
experience dating men in the past.

\n< Serena >But in reality, there is. However, I thought that
there was no way you would understand if I stayed
silent.

\n< Serena >However, my partner brought out a magic item
called the Unicorn Saddle... which determines past
dating experiences.

\n< Serena >I want you to ride this and prove that you are
truly a pure maiden...

\n< Female >How rude of a conversation is this! It makes me
angry just thinking about it!

\n< Female >There's no way you don't have any experience with
men at your age! Use common sense and think
logically!

\n< Serena >However, for an unmarried woman to have
interactions with men is considered a crime of
adultery.

\n< Serena >It's a serious crime. I've heard that depending on
the circumstances, it could even lead to beheading
or burning at the stake.

\n< Female >Hoho, that's just a facade. Nowadays, there's no
one who takes things seriously like that.
\n< Female >Yes, besides this stupid nobleman...!

\n< Female >...But even so, I can't let go of such a good
marriage proposal.

\n< Serena >So, to deceive the unicorn saddle, it's a pair of
special panties woven with a unique spirit herb...

\n< Female >Yes, researching was very difficult... but this is
where money and time come into play!

\n< Female >If I think about how the next several decades of
my life will change, I won't hesitate!
\n< Serena >I just need to procure that spirit herb, right?

\n< Female >Please. I've heard that the habitat of the spirit
herb is deep in the forest. It is said to be
located at the end of following the butterfly
adorned with blue phosphorescence.

\n< Female >But that place is also a dangerous zone where
monsters roam. It's very, very... for a weak woman
like me...

\n< Serena >Deep in the forest. The landmark is a blue
butterfly. Whether it's luring with flower
nectar... In any case, I understand. I'll go
gather it right away.

\n< Female >Oh, are you leaving already? I thought maybe we
could have some tea together or something.

\n< Serena >I'll pass. It's a simple request. I want it done
by today.

\n< Serena >It took quite a while just to listen to all of
this.

\n< Female >Oh my, ohoho, how rude of me. I got carried away
and started talking.

\n< Female >And that's because your manners and behavior are
perfect.

\n< Female >You've interpreted and responded to each of my
actions with meaning. It's been so enjoyable... I
couldn't help myself.

\n< Female >I wonder where you learned that? Your family must
have been very enthusiastic about education.

\n< Female >Your face is elegant... It's such a waste to see
you being an adventurer in a rural town like this.

\n< Female >I see. When this request is accomplished... and
when my marriage is splendidly achieved...

\n< Female >Yes, I will definitely invite you to the social
circle.

\n< Female >If it's you, you should be able to serve as a
suitable companion for a noble. If things go well,
you could even become a mistress... Depending on
the family, you might even be able to aim for the
position of a legal wife.

\n< Female >There is a single baron who lives a little north
of here. That person is quite a catch, isn't he?

\n< Female >I will definitely introduce you, so please do your
best to successfully complete the request.

\n< Serena >...If I were to tell my father that I want to
marry a baron, he would probably faint on the
spot.

\n< Female >Oh, I'm sorry. Your voice is so soft. What did you
say just now?
\n< Serena >It's nothing. Well then, I'll be going.

\n< Serena >Well... If it's this forest, it would be best to
leave the town from the south. Once I'm ready,
I'll head south.
